---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="pt-24 pb-16 px-4 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="mb-16 text-center">
        <a href="/" class="inline-block">
          <img src="/logo.svg" alt="Cebby Logo" class="h-12" />
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <div
            class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-800"
          >
            Premium Feature
          </div>
          <div
            class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium bg-green-100 text-green-800"
          >
            Coming Soon
          </div>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900">
          Performance Analytics
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Make data-driven decisions with comprehensive insights into your
          events' performance and audience engagement.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="py-16 px-4 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Engagement Tracking -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-gray-900">
          In-Depth Engagement Tracking
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          {
            [
              {
                title: "Measure What Matters",
                description:
                  "Understand how audiences engage with your events, including views, clicks, and attendance patterns. Engagement tracking offers a comprehensive look at which events draw the most attention and which platforms deliver the most interaction.",
              },
              {
                title: "Identify Key Interactions",
                description:
                  "Track RSVP rates, follow-up engagement, and interest trends over time. With Cebby's analytics, you'll gain clarity on which elements drive the highest engagement and be able to replicate successful approaches across future events.",
              },
              {
                title: "Optimize Timing and Outreach",
                description:
                  "By knowing when and where your audience is most active, you can schedule events to maximize attendance and share updates at peak engagement times.",
              },
            ].map((item) => (
              <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-900">
                  {item.title}
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">{item.description}</p>
              </div>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Audience Demographics -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-gray-900">
          Audience Demographics
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          {
            [
              {
                title: "Targeted Insights",
                description:
                  "Access detailed demographic information to better understand your audience. From age groups and geographic locations to preferred event topics, these insights help you tailor events and communications to resonate with your key attendees.",
              },
              {
                title: "Personalized Audience Engagement",
                description:
                  "With demographic breakdowns, Cebby will enable you to create targeted outreach strategies that appeal to specific segments of your audience, increasing relevance and impact.",
              },
              {
                title: "Diversity and Inclusion Metrics",
                description:
                  "Evaluate the diversity of your event attendees to ensure your events are reaching a broad, inclusive audience. This insight can help you plan initiatives that cater to a variety of backgrounds and interests, fostering a welcoming event environment.",
              },
            ].map((item) => (
              <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-900">
                  {item.title}
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">{item.description}</p>
              </div>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ROI Measurement -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-gray-900">ROI Measurement</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          {
            [
              {
                title: "Assess Your Event's Impact",
                description:
                  "Calculate return on investment (ROI) by understanding what each event contributes to your goals. Whether you're driving awareness, raising funds, or increasing membership, ROI measurement tools let you gauge the success of your events in relation to your objectives.",
              },
              {
                title: "Identify Trends and Areas for Improvement",
                description:
                  "Track spending, attendee numbers, and conversions to see how each event performs over time. With a clear view of costs versus returns, you can refine event planning strategies and make data-backed decisions for future events.",
              },
              {
                title: "Maximize Value and Efficiency",
                description:
                  "Cebby's ROI tools are designed to help you make the most of every event dollar spent. By knowing which events offer the highest returns, you can prioritize investments that deliver the best results.",
              },
            ].map((item) => (
              <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-900">
                  {item.title}
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">{item.description}</p>
              </div>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Future Analytics -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-gray-900">
          Performance Analytics: Unlock Deeper Insights
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-900">
              Future-Ready Analytics
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              With access to these analytics, you can take a data-driven
              approach to event planning, refining your strategies based on what
              works best. Over time, these insights will enhance your event
              impact, improve audience retention, and streamline your event
              planning efforts.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-900">
              Explore Future Feature Potential
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              By clicking "Performance Analytics," users can sign up for updates
              on the release and express interest in accessing this premium
              feature, emphasizing how Cebby's data-powered approach can take
              their event planning to the next level.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 px-4 bg-indigo-600">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">
        Be First to Access Premium Analytics
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg mb-8 text-indigo-100 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Join our waitlist to get early access to powerful analytics features and
        shape the future of event management.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center">
        <a
          href="https://dorelljames.notion.site/13a3f8eda0708062b70fc97987d7ba32"
          target="_blank"
          class="px-8 py-4 bg-white text-indigo-600 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-indigo-50 transition-all"
        >
          Join Waitlist
        </a>
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="px-8 py-4 border-2 border-white text-white rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-white/10 transition-all"
        >
          Learn More
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
